Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.620 --> 00:00:09.350
In this video we will learn how to create
a custom URL for Google Drive hosted website

00:00:09.350 --> 00:00:17.470
This is the default URL example
And these are short-custom URL examples

00:00:17.470 --> 00:00:39.030
Part 1, Create a custom URL using gdriv.es
First, login to google drive

00:00:39.030 --> 00:00:51.230
Go to your website folder
Copy the folder id

00:00:51.230 --> 00:01:05.330
Open a new tab
And go to gdriv.es

00:01:05.330 --> 00:01:18.150
Paste the folder id
And type the desired alias

00:01:18.150 --> 00:01:31.090
And then click the red button

00:01:31.090 --> 00:01:41.660
Your free short custom URL is ready
Part 2, Create a custom URL using gweb.io

00:01:41.660 --> 00:01:53.730
Open your browser
And go to gweb.io

00:01:53.730 --> 00:02:15.599
Click the blue button, and then login using
google username and password

00:02:15.599 --> 00:02:22.650
Select one Google Drive folder
And enter the desired custom URL

00:02:22.650 --> 00:02:37.980
And then click add

00:02:37.980 --> 00:02:46.139
Your free short custom URL is ready
Part 3, Create a custom URL using your own

00:02:46.139 --> 00:02:50.120
domain name
Open your browser

00:02:50.120 --> 00:03:04.489
And go to gweb.io
Click the blue button, and then login using

00:03:04.489 --> 00:03:23.139
google username and password

00:03:23.139 --> 00:03:30.450
Open a new tab
And go to your domain registrar, for example

00:03:30.450 --> 00:03:42.590
namecheap.com

00:03:42.590 --> 00:03:57.459
Please login to your namecheap account

00:03:57.459 --> 00:04:15.639
Go to domain manager

00:04:15.639 --> 00:04:27.270
Select "All host records"
Add or modify www.yourdomain.com CNAME record

00:04:27.270 --> 00:04:55.870
and point it to proxy.gweb.io

00:04:55.870 --> 00:05:03.800
Now back to gweb.io tab
Select one google drive folder and type your

00:05:03.800 --> 00:05:39.500
www.yourdomain.com
Your own top level domain on google drive

00:05:39.500 --> 00:05:58.900
hosted website is ready.

